{"meta":{"title":"黎擎的火柴盒","subtitle":"","description":"一个小破站...","author":"CSH215","url":"https://CSH215.github.io/CSH215","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"","date":"2024-05-05T14:49:39.083Z","updated":"2024-05-05T14:49:39.083Z","comments":true,"path":"404.html","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/404.html","excerpt":"","text":"404 很抱歉，您访问的页面不存在 可能是输入地址有误或该地址已被除"},{"title":"分类","date":"2024-05-06T09:12:03.252Z","updated":"2024-05-06T09:12:03.252Z","comments":true,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"关于","date":"2024-05-06T09:12:09.326Z","updated":"2024-05-06T09:12:09.326Z","comments":true,"path":"about/index.html","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/about/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"我的朋友们","date":"2024-05-06T09:11:54.204Z","updated":"2024-05-06T09:11:54.204Z","comments":true,"path":"friends/index.html","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/friends/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"标签","date":"2024-05-06T09:11:38.281Z","updated":"2024-05-06T09:11:38.281Z","comments":true,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"更新日志","date":"2024-05-06T09:13:42.191Z","updated":"2024-05-06T09:13:42.191Z","comments":true,"path":"updateLog/index.html","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/updateLog/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"怎么使用Hexo？？？","slug":"howUseHexo","date":"2024-05-05T11:14:27.000Z","updated":"2024-05-06T07:50:44.977Z","comments":true,"path":"2024/05/05/howUseHexo/","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/2024/05/05/howUseHexo/","excerpt":"","text":"了解Hexo什么是Hexo？ Hexo 是一个快速、简洁且高效的博客框架。Hexo 使用 Markdown（或其他标记语言）解析文章，在几秒内，即可利用靓丽的主题生成静态网页。 前提条件： Node.js (Node.js 版本需 &gt;&#x3D; 10.13，建议 Node.js 12.0 及以上版本) Git 安装Hexo npm install hexo-cli -g 更多详细教程，请自行查看Hexo官网。 注册GitHub 找到GitHub，点击 Sign up 完成注册并登录； 新建 一个仓库，用来存放你的静态Blog ； ！！！注意 ！！！ 新建仓库的名字必须跟你的GitHub的用户名一样，不能是昵称！ 假设你的用户名为Tom，你新建的GitHub仓库的名字，就必须是：Tom.github.io Tom.github.io // 必须是这个样子，否则会各种404 配置GitHub信息 配置GitHub邮箱 配置SSH密钥 Git登录 初始化Hexo文件夹 新建一个文件夹MyBlog并进入 在此文件夹中右键，Git Bash Here，进入命令行窗口 执行命令：hexo init myblog 进入你的blog文件夹：cd myblog 安装依赖：npm install 之后，运行： hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s，就可以启动服务了 而后，Ctrl+左键点击 跳出来的地址就可以看到Hexo默认页面了。","categories":[{"name":"Blog","slug":"Blog","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/categories/Blog/"},{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Blog/Hexo","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/categories/Blog/Hexo/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Blog","slug":"Blog","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/tags/Blog/"},{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/tags/Hexo/"}],"author":"CSH215"},{"title":"Hello World","slug":"hello-world","date":"2024-05-05T08:10:35.700Z","updated":"2024-05-06T07:33:25.046Z","comments":true,"path":"2024/05/05/hello-world/","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/2024/05/05/hello-world/","excerpt":"","text":"Welcome to Hexo! This is your very first post. Check documentation for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in troubleshooting or you can ask me on GitHub. Quick StartCreate a new post1$ hexo new &quot;My New Post&quot; More info: Writing Run server1$ hexo server More info: Server Generate static files1$ hexo generate More info: Generating Deploy to remote sites1$ hexo deploy More info: Deployment","categories":[{"name":"Hello","slug":"Hello","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/categories/Hello/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hello","slug":"Hello","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/tags/Hello/"}],"author":"CSH215"}],"categories":[{"name":"Blog","slug":"Blog","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/categories/Blog/"},{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Blog/Hexo","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/categories/Blog/Hexo/"},{"name":"Hello","slug":"Hello","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/categories/Hello/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Blog","slug":"Blog","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/tags/Blog/"},{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/tags/Hexo/"},{"name":"Hello","slug":"Hello","permalink":"https://csh215.github.io/CSH215/tags/Hello/"}]}